| 🔴 Critical | 1 | `Split` + LINQ + concat chain in `FixedNumberOfWordsTruncator` (~5 allocs/call) |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | Triple alloc on right-truncation path; `List<char>[]` linear scan; 3/3 classes unsealed |
